{
  "_comment": "STARTING POINT for ollama users (no SSH/MLX needed) — a light gama stack vs a bigger model, all via local ollama. NOT YET VERIFIED: swap in models you have (`ollama list`), run `python3 -m experiments.moa_vs_strong recipes/ollama-starter/config.json`, and PR your numbers into recipe.md.",
  "suite": "hard",
